{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第13回\"论战·飞战\"开篇介绍\"后人\"的两种含义，随后进入老者与少年的论道。二人共处古厝之中，老者喝茶、少年饮酒如楚留香。少年问及\"飞战\"之意，老者说那一战究竟是\"飞战\"还是\"非战\"尚无定论——因为战未开始已有一方败，而败的一方绝非楚留香。老者透露兰花先生的计划彻底失败，楚留香若死则行动如死猪无意义，若不死则必胜。最关键处不在救人，而在找出兰花先生真面目。少年指出兰花先生的弱点即在\"午夜\"与\"兰花\"——他只在月圆夜的午夜出现且必带兰花香气。老者由此讲述楚留香因鼻疾、自爱与洁癖，从遥远国度捎来郁金香香精的故事，少年叹服于香帅生前已成为传奇的缘由。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "我知道那一战被后世称为'飞战'，因为那一次行动是'飞蛾行动'，其他有关第一战的人，都有鹰之眼，鹏之翼，燕之捷，箭之确。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "他说：鹰、鹏、燕、箭，都飞，所以这一战当然是飞战。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "也许你知道的还不够多。对那一战，有两种说法。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "哪两种?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "飞翔的飞是飞，并非如此的非也是非。那一战是飞战还是非战，至今还没有人能下一个定论。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "非战?非战的意思，难道说那一战不是战?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "那一战惊天动天，天下皆知，怎么能说它不是战?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "战的意思，是针锋相对，互争胜负。可是那一战，根本就没有胜负可争。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "因为那一战还没有开始时，就已经有一方败了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "败的那一方当然不是香帅?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "当然不是。你一定要记住一点，有些人是永远都不会败的，生也不败，死也不败。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "在兰花先生的计划中，楚留香本来已经是个死定的人，出现也死，不出现也死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "我也知道是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "可是他错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这个计划是彻底失败的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "因为在这次行动中，楚留香如果已经死了，这次行动就等于没有行动。没有行动而行动，是什么呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "是猪。一条失败的猪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你说得好极了。尤其是因为今年是猪年。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "可是在这次行动中，楚留香如果没有死，就必胜无疑。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "因为一点小小的关键。这一点非常非常小的小小关键，暂时我不会告诉你的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "那么香帅有没有救出那两个人呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "当然救出来了。只不过，有没有救出那两个人并不是这次事件里最重要的关键。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "那么，最重要的关键在什么地方呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "在一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "兰花先生?是不是兰花先生?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "当然是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "如果他和这次事件这个组织完全脱离了关系，那么，这个人就要从此从这个世界上消失了，就好像从未存在过一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "所以我们一定不能让他从此消失，一定要把他的根挖出来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的。你说的话通常都非常有道理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "现在的问题只不过是要用什么法子才能挖出他的根呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "兰花先生处心积虑，掩饰自己的行踪，为的就是要保护自己，就算他这个万无一失的计划失败了，他自己也可以全身而退。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "看来他无疑是个十分谨慎小心的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "一定是的。天下枭雄人物，大都是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "只不过，他还是有弱点的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "有弱点的人，就难免会造成错误，就算不是致命的错误，至少也是一条线索。有了线索，就可以把他找出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "有理。只可惜我还不知道他的弱点在哪里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "就在午夜，就在兰花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "就在午夜，就在兰花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你说得好，只可惜我还是不懂。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "午夜的意思，就是子时左右。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这一点我懂。兰花的意思我当然也懂。这都是很容易懂的，我只不过不懂，你为什么要说它们是那个神秘人物的弱点?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "江湖传言，都说这个人只有在月圆夜的午夜时才出现，出现时总是带着一种兰花的香气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "就好像香帅出现时总是带着一种郁金香的香气一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的。江湖传言，的确如此，这种兰花的香气，最近几乎已经和香帅的郁金香的香气同样闻名了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "所以这就是他的弱点。名气有时，就像是包袱，名气越大，包袱越重。最可怕的是，这个包袱里什么都有。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "这位兰花先生平时是个非常斯文温柔的人，可是一到了月圆夜的午夜，他就变了，变成了另外一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "而且江湖中人也知道，这位兰花先生出现的时候，就好像楚留香一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "因为香帅出现的时候，总是会带着一种淡淡的香气。这位兰花先生也一样，不管他在什么时候什么地方出现，都会带着一种兰花的香气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "兰花是王者之香，难道他是王者?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "至少他自己认为是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "我想你当然应该知道楚留香这个名字的来历。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "我当然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "可是我相信你一定不知道为什么他每次出现时都要带一点香气。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "他为什么要这样做呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "因为他是一个非常自爱的人，而且有洁僻。他绝不会让别人对他留下一点坏印象。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "这是一定的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "香帅平生最痛恨的一件事，就是别人身上有臭气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "这种人谁不讨厌?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "所以香帅生怕自己身上有让别人讨厌的气味。他怕这种事，因为他自己不知道自己身上是不是有怪味。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "他嗅不出他的身上是不是有味道，他怕别人讨厌他的味道，所以他就从一个很遥远的国度，捎来一种带着郁金香的香精。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这是一个很传奇的故事。它说明一个人对自己生命的热爱与珍惜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这一类的故事，通常只会让人激动振奋，你为什么要叹息?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "因为香帅。他在活着的时候，就已经是个传奇人物，不但天下皆知，而且名留至今。我至今才知道这是怎么造成的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 292
    }
  ],
